    "In the first case, GNN-RAG retrieves both crucial facts <Gilfoyle → characters_that_have_lived_here → Toronto> and <Toronto → province.capital → Ontario> that are required to answer the question, unlike the KG-RAG baseline (RoG) that fetches only the first fact.",
